Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:39.11,eptitle,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(249,117)\c&H18347A&\2c&H213667&}Whirlwind  in  Tomomi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.69,0:01:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rise and shine, Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.41,0:02:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm so sleepy and hear such music, I become sleepier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.33,0:02:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?  A beautiful melody first thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that make you feel like something good is gonna happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be late, Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, I want one katsu sandwich !
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have a cream bun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK !  OK !  One by one.  Don't fight over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only thing left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one An-pan for the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just can't be aggressive, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do?  Everything sold out immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, if you don't hurry, the lunch break will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Kanazawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go to this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live house?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl who was supposed to go with me caught a cold, so I got one extra ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never been to that kind of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.99,0:03:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you have to come, Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. It's not that weird place. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is there some other plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The plan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet at Shibuya train station at five.  See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mikage!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mikage, are you free tonight?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kanazawa invited me to a live house...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will you come with me, Mikage?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forget it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:05:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How come?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm busy with an experiment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She said it's really fun.  Let's go Mikage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kanazawa invited you, didn't she?  You go with her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.59,0:05:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're bothering me!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hehe!  That's weird !
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks to you Tomomi, I messed up!  Stop whining and go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm late...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanazawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:05:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a moment, I thought you wouldn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... Uh... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready.  Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Ka... Kanazawa, your clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing wrong, but you have make-up on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not pretty, I won't be able to meet the band members.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!  There they are.  Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great !  She's my classmate, Tomomi Matsunaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:06:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good eveni...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you let us through?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanazawa, are you feeling OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it !
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa, here's some donuts that I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!  Donuts?  Great.  Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't live without donuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out !  Donuts, donuts, donuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it fun tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.37,0:09:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, what's keeping you?  Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm!  Tomomi is acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She definitely is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:11:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, thank you, Kanazawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good shot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Noda?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Words or music transcribed by a medium in France are typical types of automatic writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surrealists saw this as a release of the unconsciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and incorporated into their own arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomomi. Quit giggling.  I've been listening to that for a long time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Tsukasa is so great.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guitarist.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So who is he?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsunaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Older Matsunaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you smirking around?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all, teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm! Se...cret?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not hiding anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong Matsunaga?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it went to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And look what I had to go through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's the guy on the photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.  His name is Tsukasa.  He's so cool and so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some choice you got.  At least he's better than Noda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.16,0:13:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look Tomomi.  This is the tape of last night concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kanazawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi and Kanazawa?  When did they become friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cheater.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, may I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tape was awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guitar was so outrageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa's guitar is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.  I'm carrying around his pick as an amulet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I never thought you'd get into it.  I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.86,0:15:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.  I like this kind of stuff.  Let's go to a concert again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When is the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi looks so cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go for club practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda, good luck with your workout !
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problems!  I'll break more records again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaboom!  There she goes again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage hasn't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey watch your mouth.  I'm here you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong Mikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not feeling good so I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then whose explosion was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be Kageura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Tomomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Tomomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, 50 laps of dashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.31,0:16:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.09,0:16:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act surprised!  The music is too noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the band?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just wanted to see how other bands are like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you'd do that with your headphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:16:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H101360&}This segment describes the desolate feelings of the poet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H101360&}For this poet, what was the home like?  And how did he feel about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H101360&}Now pay attention to the fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H101360&\q2}that this is the home that he has finally reached\N after long and treacherous travels, and read it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H101360&}Well then, let us examine the usage of adjectives and adverbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H101360&}Let's see, Kobayashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda, no club activities today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm supposed to take Yamagishi to a ramen place that I owe him.  Right, Yamagishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.  See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mikage, are you still up?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kanazawa was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm tired because of lab experiments.  Let me sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomomi, go to sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, I got the tickets for the next concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can see Tsukasa again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kanazawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll play a new song.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?  I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my gosh!  I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have your autographs, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.  Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't enough. Tomomi, can I have ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheapskate...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bleah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.65,0:20:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to a concert next week right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so fun about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.59,0:21:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.84,0:21:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miracle Girls here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Mikage dating with Noda?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can we do?  Our minds got swapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:22:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Miracle Girls, "Mysterious Moving High Love Pressure"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.53,0:22:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ought to kiss for Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.64,0:22:12.15,notes,note,0000,0000,0046,,{\a6}Original air date Mar 26, 1993.
